<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̹dyny ạ̉mạnẗ lyk wqt ạlạ̹ymạn
 mạ yumtḥn
 wạḥmyny bmḥbẗ lyk ạ̉ḥyạ bqdạsẗ wqt ạlmḥn
 ạlqrạr- wạlnʿmẗ ạlly mạlkẗ qlby bạlbr
 wạlḍyạʾ
 tʿln ạ̹n ạ̹nt rby fy ḥyạty kmạ fy ạlsmạʾ
 2- ạ̹dyny ạ̉mạnẗ lyk fy ạlṣgẖyr wạlqlyl
 wạ̉zyd mtdạry fyk wạltẖmạr tbqy̱ ạldlyl
 3- ạ̹dyny ạ̉mạnẗ lyk fy ạlwkạlẗ ʿly̱ ạlḥyạẗ
 wạ̉ʿysẖ lywm mjyỷk mtḥạwṭ btrs ạlrḍạ</lyrics>
<title>ạ̹dyny ạ̉mạnẗ</title>
